description:
The official EXO light stick (Version 3.0) can be connected to your smartphone via Bluetooth 4.0.
In the package you will find additional items including a white envelope with a group photo card, one sheet of 10 stickers composed of one logo sticker and 9 stickers featuring a name of a single member with a corresponding number (all members are present: Suho (1), Baekhyun (4), Lay (10), D.O. (12), Chen (21), Chanyeol (61), Kai (88), Sehun (94) and Xiumin (99)), a user manual and a warranty card with a sticker of authenticity from SM Entertainment. You will also get a white hand strap and, as I mentioned before, a silver cover. All comes in a white box of approximately the same size as the box containing the previous version of the EXO light stick. The size of the box is 130 x 50 x 311 mm.

When it comes to uniqueness, BLACKPINK's hammer lightstick or 'BI-Ping-Bong' is definitely one of the top contenders. 
Content + Care:
-Light Mode: On, Blink, Flicker, Off
-Maximum Operation: 5 Hours
-Power: 3AAA Batteries
-Weight: 1.5lbs /680g
-Concert light syncing feature / Changes color
